
# **README - Top Movies API Project**  

Online URL: [https://varleenbiketi.github.io/Web-development-projects/API_Usage/apiData.html]

## **Project Overview**  
This project utilizes the **OMDb API** to fetch and display movie data dynamically using JavaScript and the `fetch` API. The webpage lists the top movies based on a search query and provides details such as title, year, type, and IMDb ID.  

